transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan?
Executive: Haan sir, maine sir yaha pe image aapka add kar diya hai. To 24 se 48 ghante mein wo aapka show hone lagega.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Ji. Dekha ya to aap matlab batao fir main concern close kar du?
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Main bol rahi hu ki main apna concern close kar du? Kyuki aapne mere number pe call nahi kiya tha na?
Customer: Ji.

Executive: Thik hai kar dijiye na.
Executive: Thik hai, main close kar de rahi hu. Aapke pass ho sakta hai feedback ke liye koi mail aaye.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Ji. To waha pe yes kar dijiyega.
Customer: Ji.
summary:

- Executive wants to close the concern.



Resolution:

- Executive added the image and closed the concern.

None
